To install this simple image gallery, follow these steps:

	* Copy the module folder to your kohana modules directory, and name it 'sigal'
	* Add MODPATH.'sigal' to your module list in bootstrap.php
	* Copy the media-folder contents to where your asset-folder
	* Copy config/sigal.php to your application folder, and configure it for your environment
	* Chmod 777 the gallery upload path, defined in your config.
	* Execute TABLES.SQL for your database tables (and modify if you changed the table variables in the config)

OPTIONAL
	* Copy the routes 'sigal-frontend' & 'sigal-backend' to your bootstrap.php
	* Have fun!

